# Livewire Widget Rules
- use "livewire.admin.widget" prefix for widget components
- use "https://mary-ui.com" as the source of the components
- dont make extra css or javascript for the components
- make the components responsive
- use alpinejs for the components if needed
- use tailwindcss for the components with daisyui
- write code block comments in the components for the readability
- write the components optionally with the inputs


